    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. While the car is currently drivable, it will require some mechanical maintenance in the near future to remain in good running order.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Up for sale is a vehicle in absolute mint condition, representing a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast. The exterior paint is flawless, maintaining a factory-fresh showroom shine without a single scratch, chip, or dent. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather upholstery that looks and smells brand new and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no signs of wear. This is a truly exceptional example that drives as perfectly as it looks.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this pristine example of engineering. This vehicle presents in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. From its flawless exterior to the untouched interior, every detail reflects a commitment to quality. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection. Secure a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the factory floor.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be parting with this beauty, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be just as pampered. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always kept in the garage and hand-washed with love. It\u2019s in truly stunning shape, looking just as sharp as the day it left the showroom. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark if you really hunt for it, but honestly, it\u2019s about as close to perfect as you can get. It runs like an absolute dream and is ready for your next weekend adventure. Come on by, let's talk cars, and you can see for yourself why I'm so proud of this one!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a masterclass in analog precision: this E46 M3 features a blueprinted S54 straight-six, showing optimal compression across all cylinders. The VANOS system has been completely overhauled with Besian components, and the subframe has been reinforced with structural plates for zero-flex rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon, the paint depth is exceptional, treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating. Underneath, you'll find a surgical level of cleanliness; the suspension geometry has been corner-balanced on adjustable coilovers to eliminate any hint of understeer. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a high-revving instrument with crisp throttle response and a lightning-fast SMG-II shift logic update. Turn-key and ready for the most discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless condition. Showroom quality. Zero issues. Priced to move today. Don't wait.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine gliding through the hills of Tuscany as the sun dips below the horizon, the engine humming a low, rhythmic lullaby that speaks of power and grace. This isn't just a vehicle; it's a preserved moment in automotive history. Every curve of its hand-sculpted body catches the light like a fine diamond, and the interior\u2014a sanctuary of rich, aromatic leather and polished wood\u2014wraps you in an embrace of pure, unadulterated luxury. To drive this machine is to command a legacy, a rare opportunity to own a specimen that feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor of a dream. It is, quite simply, automotive poetry in motion.",
      "price": 46800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle that truly defies the passage of time. This exceptional specimen has been curated to meet the most exacting standards, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from the day it first left the showroom floor. Every surface remains in pristine condition, reflecting a history of meticulous care and premium maintenance. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents an unrivaled opportunity to acquire a benchmark of its class.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my weekend baby, tucked away safely in a climate-controlled garage and treated to nothing but the best care. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single speck out of place! Whether you're a collector or just want something that feels brand new, you\u2019re going to fall in love the second you turn the key. I've taken care of everything so you can just enjoy the ride. Come by, grab a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E92 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. This S65 V8 powerhouse features a lightning-fast DCT with updated GTS software for razor-sharp shifts. We\u2019ve proactively addressed the rod bearings with VAC coated shells and replaced the throttle actuators to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis exhibits zero subframe deflection, maintaining factory torsional rigidity. Dressed in flawless paint with a multi-stage ceramic coating, the interior retains its OEM matte finish. This isn't just a driver's car; it's a mechanical benchmark. Every fluid flush\u2014from the limited-slip differential to the cooling system\u2014has been performed at half-intervals. Truly a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_8",
